HubSpot,is,an,internet,company,that,provides,high,quality,internet,marketing,to,small,internet,based,businesses,HubSpot,transforms,relatively,static,small,business,websites,into,modern,marketing,machines,that,produce,the,right,leads,and,helps,convert,a,higher,percentage,of,businesses,into,qualified,opportunities,The,HubSpot,Blog,API,is,a,RESTful,API,that,allows,users,and,developers,to,create,view,and,access,HubSpot,Blog,data,outside,of,the,normal,HubSpot,user,interface,The,HubSpot,Blog,API,is,currently,in,Beta,it,is,not,complete,or,mature,yet